### Wolverine Messaging PoC - API Tests
### Use with VS Code REST Client extension or similar

@baseUrl = http://localhost:5000

### Get API information
GET {{baseUrl}}/

### Create an order
# @name createOrder
POST {{baseUrl}}/orders
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "customerName": "John Doe",
  "items": ["Laptop", "Mouse", "Keyboard"],
  "totalAmount": 1299.99
}

### Get the created order ID
@orderId = {{createOrder.response.body.$.id}}

### Get all orders
GET {{baseUrl}}/orders

### Get order by ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/orders/{{orderId}}

### Ship the order
POST {{baseUrl}}/orders/{{orderId}}/ship

### Cancel an order (create a new one first)
POST {{baseUrl}}/orders
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "customerName": "Jane Smith",
  "items": ["Phone Case"],
  "totalAmount": 29.99
}

